channel.title: Webclient [PI]
channel.description: I made my own JAR file and it auto downloads the cache. I just need to know how to upload it to my forumation forums. I know that you go into the HTML page, but what do you do with the text document and what do you put in it. What else do you upload to dropbox other than the cache?

item.title: Webclient [PI]
item.dc:creator: @Onix Onix
item.description:
@Onix wrote:

[quote=“AtomicInt_, post:4, topic:444329”]Nothing. You don’t need to do anything with this ‘text document’.

All you need to do is upload the jar to your website, then write out a html template to load the jar.[/quote]Also, if you can’t write your own HTML template, there are some tutorials for this. Just look around in the tutorials section.
